This is a wikistats (cloud) instance.

After applying the puppet role for the first time you
have to deploy the wikistats app files.

run 'deploy-wikistats deploy'

deploy-wikistats <action>

deploy: syncs file from /srv/wikistats (where puppet git pulls to automatically) into the right places.

backup: syncs files currently used to a backup location at /usr/lib/wikistats/backup.

restore: syncs file from the backup location {/usr/lib/wikistats/backup} into the right places.

